<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These tools connect to your wallets via API. They act as a crypto wallet tracker, pulling in every trade, deposit, and withdrawal. They then apply tax logic (</span><a href="https://www.investopedia.com/articles/02/060502.asp" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIFO, LIFO</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">) to calculate your capital gains.</span></p>
