<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This is a key feature of the best portfolio tracker crypto tools. Tax loss harvesting involves selling assets at a loss to offset your gains. A crypto portfolio tracker like CoinLedger or Koinly will identify these opportunities for you, potentially saving you thousands.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What Features Should I Look for When Choosing Crypto Tax Software?</span></h2>
