<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">DeFi &amp; NFT Tax Software Capabilities</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you are into NFTs, a standard crypto and stock portfolio tracker might fail. You need a specialized best DeFi portfolio tracker like ZenLedger that understands smart contracts.</span></p>
