										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every prop firm advertises a big profit-split number. Far fewer let you reach it without a paid upgrade, a specific payout schedule, or a loyalty tier you may never hit. A &#8220;100 percent split&#8221; that requires an add-on and a 30-day wait is not the same as a 90 percent split that lands in your wallet within a day.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This ranking judges the highest payout crypto prop firm options in 2026 on effective payout, not headline marketing: the split you can realistically reach, how fast it pays, and whether a time limit pressures you into bad trades. A crypto prop firm no time limit policy matters here, because the freedom to wait for clean setups protects the account that produces the payout in the first place. Every figure is approximate and current as of mid-2026, so verify each claim directly before paying.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">The 8 Highest Payout Crypto Prop Firms in 2026&#8243;</span></h2>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">1. Crypto Fund Trader (CFT)</span></h3>
