<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">CFT leads on effective payout rather than a flashy ceiling. Its split is 80 percent upgradable to a clean 90 percent, and the payout itself is documented in the 8 to 24 hour range in crypto or by bank transfer, among the faster cycles in the sector. Evaluations carry no time pressure to force the account, and execution runs on real Bybit order books with leverage up to 1:100. See current programs at</span><a href="https://cryptofundtrader.com/?utm_source=ventureburn&amp;utm_medium=pr&amp;utm_campaign=june26" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Crypto Fund Trader</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Watch-outs: a $10,000 daily profit cap shapes how fast a big day compounds, and you should confirm current eligibility and the firm&#8217;s status before paying. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A strong fit for</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">  traders who want a reachable 90 percent and fast withdrawals over a headline number with strings attached.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">2. Breakout</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_203034" style="width: 1912px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203034" class="wp-image-203034 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/image3-1.jpg" alt="Screenshot of the Breakout homepage, the only crypto prop firm owned by US-regulated exchange Kraken. " width="1902" height="943" /><p id="caption-attachment-203034" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Breakout</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Breakout pairs a clean 80 to 90 percent split with the fastest payout structure here: on-demand USDC withdrawals around the clock, including multiple per day. There are no consistency rules and no minimum trading days, so nothing gates the payout artificially, and the Kraken backing adds trust. The 90 percent is straightforward rather than buried behind paid tiers.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Watch-outs: conservative, non-customizable leverage. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A strong fit for</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">  traders who prioritize payout speed and a transparent path to 90 percent.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">3. HyroTrader</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_203033" style="width: 1911px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203033" class="wp-image-203033 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/image1-2.jpg" alt="Screenshot of the HyroTrader homepage, a crypto-exclusive prop firm executing through Bybit and Binance. " width="1901" height="1080" /><p id="caption-attachment-203033" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Hyrotrader</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">HyroTrader climbs from around 70 percent toward 90 percent through milestones, and it sweetens net payout in a way few firms do: the evaluation fee is refunded with your first payout, which effectively raises what you keep early on. Withdrawals process on demand in roughly 12 to 24 hours, with exchange-native execution behind them.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Watch-outs: a stricter rulebook with a mandatory stop-loss. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A strong fit for</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">  traders who value a refunded fee and exchange-native settlement on the road to 90 percent.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">4. DNA Funded</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_203037" style="width: 1913px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203037" class="wp-image-203037 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/image5-1.jpg" alt="Screenshot of the DNA Funded homepage, a budget crypto prop firm built on the TradeLocker platform. " width="1903" height="944" /><p id="caption-attachment-203037" class="wp-caption-text">Source: DNA Funded</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">DNA Funded offers an 80 percent split upgradable to 90 percent through a boost, with no time limit on its simple one-step evaluation and transparent drawdown rules. Low entry fees mean the cost of reaching that split is modest, and the TradingView-native platform keeps friction down.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Watch-outs: a younger firm with a still-building payout record. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A strong fit for</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> budget traders who want a reachable 90 percent without a large upfront fee.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">5. Hola Prime</span></h3>
<div id="attachment_203039" style="width: 1913px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203039" class="wp-image-203039 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/image7.jpg" alt="Screenshot of the Hola Prime homepage, a prop firm known for payouts as fast as one hour. " width="1903" height="898" /><p id="caption-attachment-203039" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Hola Prime</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hola Prime headlines an 80 percent split rising toward 95 percent, but the higher number comes through loyalty bonuses earned over time rather than from day one. Where it genuinely shines is speed: payouts are sometimes processed in as little as one hour, and scaling runs toward $4 million.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Watch-outs: the 95 percent is loyalty-gated, so the effective early split is closer to 80 percent. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A strong fit for</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">  traders who prize fast withdrawals and will trade through cycles to lift the split.</span></p>
