<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">FundedNext reaches up to 95 percent and adds an unusual perk: a 15 percent performance reward from the evaluation phase paid with the first funded withdrawal. The maximum advertised profit split is conditional, and crypto itself is a narrow part of its multi-asset lineup, but the firm&#8217;s disclosed payout scale is large. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Watch-outs: the highest split depends on plan and conditions, and crypto pairs are limited. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A strong fit for</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">  multi-asset traders who want a high headline split with documented payouts.</span></p>
